{"event":"message.received","sessionId":"ws_ofk3zzwp","messageId":"AC38871EB828354006F3CADF5A860B7F","chat":"120363424705809527@g.us","sender":"171407984054526@lid","from":"171407984054526","text":"Today Task Report\nDate 25/06/2026\nProject  -- Green Wash Co. \n\n🌿 Brand Identity & App Re-branding (2 Hours)\n* Successfully rebranded the application from **Difwa** to **Green Wash Co.**\n* Updated Android app name in `AndroidManifest.xml`.\n* Generated and applied Android & iOS launcher icons using custom `app_logo.png`.\n* Updated branding configurations and verified implementation across platforms.\n🖼️ Global Logo Integration (2 Hours)\n* Integrated `app_logo.png` into the Splash Screen.\n* Updated Login Page (`mobile_login_page.dart`) branding.\n* Updated Home Screen Header (`home_header.dart`) branding.\n* Integrated logo into the About Page.\n* Updated `app_images.dart` constants for centralized asset management.\n* Verified branding consistency throughout the application.\n        UI/UX Enhancements (2 Hours)\n* Improved product card interactions on Home Page and Exclusive Packages page.\n* Modified package image click behavior to open Product Details Page.\n* Restricted add-to-cart functionality exclusively to the `+` button.\n* Refactored the Profile page \"Rate Us\" feature.\n* Developed and integrated an interactive In-App Star Rating Dialog.\n* Implemented 1–5 star rating selection and submission functionality.\n       Bug Fixes & Stability Improvements (2 Hours)\n* Fixed critical syntax and compilation issues in `home_page.dart`.\n* Resolved bracket mismatch errors.\n* Fixed `Too many positional arguments` errors in `Text()` widgets.\n* Fixed subscription toggle state management issue on My Subscriptions page.\n* Resolved `PathNotFoundException` caused by missing asset references.\n* Fixed Plan Details bottom sheet overflow issues.\n* Corrected image loading by replacing improper `Image.network` usage with `Image.asset`.\n* Implemented scrollable bottom sheet support for smaller devices.\n* Conducted final testing and validation of all completed tasks.","type":"text","pushName":"Ankur Sir","isGroup":true,"timestamp":"2026-06-25T13:36:48Z"}
